domain.description: Polar chart subplots are not supported yet. This key has currently no effect.

showticklabels.description: Determines whether or not the radial axis ticks will feature tick labels.

orientation.description: Sets the orientation (an angle with respect to the origin) of the radial axis.

ticklen.description: Sets the length of the tick lines on this radial axis.

visible.description: Determines whether or not this axis will be visible.

range.description: Defines the start and end point of this radial axis.

ticksuffix.description: Sets the length of the tick lines on this radial axis.

tickcolor.description: Sets the color of the tick lines on this radial axis.

showline.description: Determines whether or not the line bounding this radial axis will be shown on the figure.

tickorientation.description: Sets the orientation (from the paper perspective) of the radial axis tick labels.
